Basic Calculator Version 1.2.0
===========================================

Release Date: January 16, 2026

This is version 1.2.0 with comprehensive calculator features and robust implementation.

FEATURES:
---------
✓ Expression-based mathematical calculations
✓ Full parentheses support with proper operator precedence
✓ Persistent calculation history with scrollable display
✓ Independent display and button scaling
✓ Window size memory across sessions
✓ Complete keyboard support for all operations
✓ Professional UI with compact button design
✓ Settings persistence for precision and display preferences
✓ Support for complex mathematical expressions
✓ Error handling and validation

TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS:
-------------------------
- Language: C with GTK+ 3.0
- Build system: GNU Make
- Dependencies: GTK+ 3.0, GLib, Cairo, Pango
- Platform: Linux (tested on CachyOS)
- Architecture: x86_64

USAGE:
------
Compile: make
Run: ./calculator
Clean: make clean

The calculator supports both mouse and keyboard input for all operations.

CHANGELOG:
----------
v1.2.0 - Advanced Calculator Release
- Dynamic precision for small numbers with significant digit display
- Comprehensive error handling and validation
- Memory safety improvements and leak prevention
- Enhanced operator input validation
- Robust expression parsing with stack overflow protection
- Professional UI with responsive scaling
- Complete keyboard and mouse input support
- Settings persistence for all preferences

v1.1.0 - Enhanced Features
- Advanced operator validation and syntax checking
- Improved parentheses handling after operators
- Unary operator support and negative numbers
- Fresh calculation start functionality
- Enhanced display buffer management

v1.0.0 - Initial Release
- Expression-based mathematical calculations
- Full parentheses support with operator precedence
- Persistent calculation history with scrollable display
- Independent display and button scaling
- Window size memory across sessions
- Complete keyboard support for all operations
- Professional UI with compact button design
- Settings persistence for precision and display preferences